{"word":"συνεφάπτομαι","slug":"συνεφάπτομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συνεφάπτομαι</b></el> <el>(ionic <el>συνεπ</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-άψομαι</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>:<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> rei, <i>to take part in</i>, <el>ἔργου</el> <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>; <el>τοὺς συνεφαπτομένους</el> <i>those who take part in</i> [the war], <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to join</i> one <i>in attacking</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}